      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or as a major restoration project. It currently has a non-functioning transmission and the engine requires a complete overhaul to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows heavy wear, including significant rust spots and faded paint, while the interior has several tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is ideal for a mechanic or hobbyist looking for a challenge or specific components, as it will require towing and extensive repairs before it can be driven.",
