      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine, showroom-quality vehicle! This car is in mint condition, meticulously maintained to look and drive just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. Every detail is flawless, from the sparkling exterior to the spotless interior, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a like-new experience without the brand-new price tag. Don't miss out on this rare find\u2014it's truly a gem!",
