      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously preserved 1995 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering. Powered by the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary, this unit exhibits exceptional compression and a pristine vacuum system. The five-speed manual gearbox shifts with mechanical precision, channeling torque through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Its double-wishbone suspension remains tight, preserving the celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in its original pigment with zero oxidation, the interior features flawless upholstery and a crack-free",
