    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This car features factory-original paint that retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. The interior is equally immaculate; the premium hand-stitched leather remains supple with zero signs of wear, and the cabin still carries that new-car scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history documenting every scheduled maintenance performed by master technicians. It has been meticulously garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of obsessive care. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example available on the market today.",
